# This directory is regenerated by the frac_dsp_busmux task. Only two files are
# tracked as golden references and diffed by basic_reg_test.sh:
#   - bitstream_distribution.xml  : per-block configuration-bit counts
#   - lb/logical_tile_mult_32_mode_mult_32x32__mult_32x32_slice.v
#       : the DSP tile netlist, used to verify the bus mux shared config bit
#         (one shared memory feeding all 32 per-bit muxes)
# Everything else written by write_fabric_verilog is ignored.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/bitstream_distribution.xml
!/lb
/lb/*
!/lb/logical_tile_mult_32_mode_mult_32x32__mult_32x32_slice.v
